<collectingCountry id="11E57608FFFB5F5FFD1CFEDF7E01B27B" box="[754,793,271,298]" name="Philippines" pageId="9" pageNumber="404">PH</collectingCountry>
0.20, PPL 0.09, PPW 0.27, PPH 0.20, ESL 0.09, ESD 0.20, HTL 0.33, total length ca. 2.4.
</paragraph>
<caption id="3D8D6610FFFB5F5FFF42F9327CDEB419" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6449299" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6449299" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6449299/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="404" startId="9.[172,211,1762,1784]" targetBox="[217,1181,429,1704]" targetPageId="9">
<paragraph id="694D3698FFFB5F5FFF42F9327CDEB419" blockId="9.[172,1231,1762,1864]" pageId="9" pageNumber="404">
